        },
        {
          "label": "(3)",
          "token": "3",
          "kind": "numeric",
          "text": "If formation is approved, any election required by ORS 198.810 to 198.825 shall be dispensed with. After the hearing on the petition, if the county board approves the petition, it shall enter an order creating the district. If the district board members generally are elected, the persons nominated by the petition and accepting nomination as members of the board shall constitute the first board of the district.",
          "subsections": []
        }
